<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.4.5">
<l>cuṟṟiniṉ ṟāyarta ḻaika ḷiṭac</l>
<l rend="indent">curuḷpaṅki nēttirat tāla ṇintu</l>
<l>paṟṟiniṉ ṟāyarka ṭaitta laiyē</l>
<l rend="indent">pāṭavu māṭakaṇ ṭēṉaṉ ṟippiṉ</l>
<l>maṟṟoru varkkeṉṉaip pēca loṭṭēṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">māliruñ cōlaiyem māyaṟ kallāl</l>
<l>koṟṟava ṉukkiva ḷāmeṉ ṟeṇṇik</l>
<l rend="indent">koṭumiṉkaḷ koṭīrā kilkō ḻampamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I watched as he sang and danced,</l>
<l rend="indent">getting and staying in front of the herders,</l>
<l>adorned by the eye of a peacock feather in [his] curly hair,</l>
<l rend="indent">while herders stood around [him] with fans of peacock feathers.</l>
<l>Hereafter, I cannot tolerate talk of me [being]</l>
<l rend="indent">for any other except for our Māyaṉ of Māliruñcōlai.</l>
<l>Considering that she belongs to the Victor, give [her to him]!</l>
<l rend="indent">If [you] do not give [her], there will be trouble!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
